sub_fields.label: Image
sub_fields.name: image
sub_fields.instructions: This image must be larger than 500x500.

sub_fields.label: Module Settings
sub_fields.name: module_settings
sub_fields.instructions: You've already created a Section. Now, fill it up with content, column by column. If you just want one column, select Full Width. If you'd like 3 columns, for example, create 3 columns with 1/3 width.

sub_fields.label: Images
sub_fields.name: images
sub_fields.instructions: Add images here that ideally have a 3:2 resolution ratio.

sub_fields.label: Add Video?
sub_fields.name: add_video
sub_fields.instructions: Toggle this on to add a video popup to this image.

sub_fields.label: Video Embed Code
sub_fields.name: video_embed_code
sub_fields.instructions: Enter the iframe embed code here from the external video hosting platform.
sub_fields.placeholder: <iframe width="560" height="315" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/NpEaa2P7qZI" title="YouTube video player" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe>

sub_fields.label: Navigation Items
sub_fields.name: navigation_items
sub_fields.instructions: Each one of these in-page navigation items' Custom ID needs to correspond to a page builder element's Custom ID setting which you can find in each one's Advanced Module Settings.

sub_fields.label: Element ID
sub_fields.name: element_id
sub_fields.instructions: This should not include the hashtag. Example: content.

sub_fields.label: Slides
sub_fields.name: slides
sub_fields.instructions: If your Mainstage Area includes the option for a slideshow then you will be able to add multiple slides here. If not, the maximum number of slides you can add will be 1.

sub_fields.label: Buttons
sub_fields.name: buttons
sub_fields.instructions: If your website doesn't support multiple buttons then you will only be able to add a maximum of 1.

sub_fields.label: Newsroom Archive

sub_fields.instructions: If your Mainstage Area includes the option for a slideshow then you will be able to add multiple slides here. If not, the maximum number of slides you can add will be 1.
